long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
Easily find and switch between too many open tabs.

Shortcuts:

Open Tabular:
Ctrl/Cmd + Shift + K

Close selected tab:
Ctrl/Cmd + D

Move selection up:
Ctrl/Cmd + K
or
Up arrow key

Move Selection down:
Ctrl/Cmd + J
or
Down arrow key

Close Tabular:
Esc
